text: São Nicolau () was a civil parish in the municipality of Porto, Portugal. In 2013, the parish merged into the new parish Cedofeita, Santo Ildefonso, Sé, Miragaia, São Nicolau e Vitória. The population in 2011 was 1,906,Instituto Nacional de Estatística in an area of 0.25 km².Eurostat ==References== Category:Porto Category:Parishes
